Packages 
Package Description
tinfour.common
Provides classes and interfaces that are common to multiple packages within the TinFour project.
tinfour.gwr
Supports Geographically Weighted Regression (GWR) methods of interpolation .
tinfour.interpolation
Provides interfaces and supporting classes for performing interpolation over TINs
tinfour.las
Provides classes and definitions for reading lidar files.
tinfour.standard
Provides classes and interfaces for creating a Triangulated Irregular Network (TIN) based on the Delaunay Triangulation specification.
tinfour.utils
Provides both high-level and general utilities for using the Tinfour packages.
tinfour.virtual
Provides classes and interfaces for creating a Triangulated Irregular Network (TIN) based on the Delaunay Triangulation specification and using a virtual representation of edges to reduce memory requirements.
tinfour.vividsolutions.jts.math
A temporary package providing tools from the JTS Topology Suite.
